  "text": "A device has been developed which delivers temperature-controlled radiofrequency energy to the anorectal junction to treat fecal incontinence. [CITATION_1] The procedure is performed as an outpatient either in the endoscopy suite or ambulatory surgery center. A submucosal radiofrequency energy is delivered circumferentially to the anorectal junction.",
